## Comprehensive Report: Transformers.js Pipeline Patterns

Based on my thorough exploration of the Transformers.js codebase, here's a complete guide to understanding and creating new pipelines:

### 1. MAIN PIPELINES FILE LOCATION

**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775484887743-rqy0c4/src/pipelines.js`

